Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [укажи дату публикации]

This website ("cosmifystellara.netlify.app") is operated by Cosmify Stellara. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect non-personal information such as browser type, operating system, and pages visited. If you use our contact form, we may collect your name and email address.

2. Use of Cookies
This site uses cookies to improve user experience and support advertising via Google AdSense. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.

3. Third-Party Services
We use Google AdSense to display ads. These services may collect data to personalize content and measure performance. Please refer to [Google’s Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy) for more details.

4. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.

5. Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via the form on this website.

6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.
